ActCustoms Tariff
SubjectOrder Repealing Certain Regulations and Orders Made Under the Customs Tariff (CUSMA)
PrecisOrder repealing CERTAIN REGULATIONS AND ORDERS MADE UNDER THE CUSTOMS TARIFF (CUSMA) in order to repeal a number of Customs Tariff orders and regulations that will be obsolete once the Canada-United States-Mexico Agreement (CUSMA) supersedes the North American Free Trade Agreement (NAFTA).
